" You can edit this file by hand.
" The " character at the beginning of a line comments out the line.
" Blank lines are ignored.

" The Default color scheme is used for any directory that does not have
" a specified scheme and for parts of user interface like menus. A
" color scheme set for a base directory will also
" be used for the sub directories.

" The standard ncurses colors are:
" Default = -1 = None, can be used for transparency or -1 color
" Black = 0
" Red = 1
" Green = 2
" Yellow = 3
" Blue = 4
" Magenta = 5
" Cyan = 6
" White = 7

" Light versions of colors are also available (set bold attribute):
" LightBlack
" LightRed
" LightGreen
" LightYellow
" LightBlue
" LightMagenta
" LightCyan
" LightWhite

" Available attributes (some of them can be combined):
" bold
" underline
" reverse or inverse
" standout
" italic (on unsupported systems becomes reverse)
" none

" Vifm supports 256 colors you can use color numbers 0-255
" (requires properly set up terminal: set your TERM environment variable
" (directly or using resources) to some color terminal name (e.g.
" xterm-256color) from /usr/lib/terminfo/; you can check current number
" of colors in your terminal with tput colors command)

" hi group cterm=attrs ctermfg=foreground_color ctermbg=background_color

hi clear

hi Win cterm=none ctermfg=white ctermbg=-1
hi Directory cterm=none ctermfg=cyan ctermbg=-1
hi Link cterm=none ctermfg=yellow ctermbg=-1
hi BrokenLink cterm=none ctermfg=red ctermbg=-1
hi Socket cterm=none ctermfg=magenta ctermbg=-1
hi Device cterm=none ctermfg=red ctermbg=-1
hi Fifo cterm=none ctermfg=cyan ctermbg=-1
hi Executable cterm=none ctermfg=green ctermbg=-1
hi Selected cterm=reverse ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
hi CurrLine cterm=bold,reverse ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
hi TopLine cterm=none ctermbg=236 ctermfg=15
hi TopLineSel cterm=bold ctermfg=15 ctermbg=-1
hi StatusLine cterm=bold ctermbg=236 ctermfg=15
hi WildMenu cterm=underline,reverse ctermfg=white ctermbg=black
hi CmdLine cterm=none ctermfg=white ctermbg=black
hi ErrorMsg cterm=none ctermfg=red ctermbg=black
hi Border cterm=none ctermfg=15 ctermbg=236
hi JobLine cterm=bold,reverse ctermfg=black ctermbg=white
hi SuggestBox cterm=bold ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
hi CmpMismatch cterm=bold ctermfg=white ctermbg=red
hi AuxWin cterm=bold,underline,reverse,standout,italic ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
hi TabLine cterm=none ctermfg=white ctermbg=black
hi TabLineSel cterm=bold,reverse ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
hi User1 cterm=bold,underline,reverse,standout,italic ctermfg=-1 ctermbg=-1
